title: Early voting at Colleyville City Hall - Oct. 19-30 (City of Colleyville, TX)
text: ( Source : City of Colleyville, TX ) Colleyville City Hall , 100 Main St ., will serve as an early voting location for the November elections. Voting takes place on the second floor. Get dates and times here. Monday-Friday, Oct. 19-23 8:00
